<td align="right"><small class="editlink noprint plainlinksneverexpand"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Thermodynamic_equations&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Thermodynamic_equations&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">edit</a></small></td>
